title: Jake Owen Stops By & Breaks News That He’ll Sing At A Country Couple’s Wedding + Amy Gives Update On Her Sick Daughter

description:
Jake Owen stops by for The Friday Morning Conversation and breaks news that he was asked to sing at a country couple’s upcoming wedding. Amy gives an update on her sick daughter. Also, Lunchbox shares a Baby Box Update.
